create src and dist folder
index.html create the ui and added two buttons
index.js intially its showing no boxes message
Add Box button adds a new box
Each new box will have a count number assigned
on click Add Box Alternating box will be in blue and black color
Total Count of boxes is show below the stack
Font Size of the Total Count increases with box count
Also, every 5th box (5, 10, 15, etc) has an Orange border on top
On clicking Remove box, removes the last box
When you no boxes remain, a message appears
